features: 5 in 1 Worldwide Travel Adapter with USB: This universal travel adaptor provides a worldwide AC outlet and 4 USB charging ports. 2 USB A and 2 USB C in total 21W can meet your need to charge multi devices. Ideal for charging your phones, laptops, tablets, cameras and more

Universal Plug Adaptor UK to World: Our international power adapter has 4 different plugs, which covers over 224 countries. You can use it in Europe, USA, UK, Spain, France, Germany, Greece, Italy, Thailand, Japan, Asia, Australia, etc. (NOT for South Africa and India)

Compact for Traveling: With size of 5 x 5.3 x 7.1 cm and weight of 149 g, TESSAN universal adapter plug travel can save a lot of space in your luggage without having to take many travel adapters on your trip
Double Protection: This European plug adapter was built in double 10A fuse, an extra fuse included, which can provide double protection for you

Instructions for Use: The usb travel adapter is not a voltage converter. International plug adaptor only suitable for devices with dual voltages or global devices with an input voltage range of 100 to 250V
description: Product Description Previous page Next page 1 Covers Over 224 Countries 2 All in 1 Design 3 2 USB A, 2 USB C 4 Meet Your Charging Need 2 USB C and 2 USB A Internatioanl Plug Adaptor The 2 USB C ports can charge up to 3.0A/15W, and the 2 USB A ports can charge up to 2.4A/12W. This usb travel adapter is ideal for your USB devices. All the USB ports output: 4.2A/21W max. Instructions for Use The international travel adapter is not a voltage converter. It is only suitable for devices with dual voltages or global devices with an input voltage range of 100 to 250V. Please check your devices voltage before use. Extra Spare Fuse This travel plug adapter provides 2 fuses for you. You can change the fuse when it stops working, bringing double protection for your trip. Travel Adaptor with Compact Size When travelling overseas, we always want to take lots of stuffs.. Sometimes there is no much space. So stuffs with smaller size is the better choice. TESSAN worldwide travel adapter with usb is compact and lightweight, and can easily put in your luggage or suitcases or be taken aboard cruise ship.
